19namespace ZXing {
20
21class BitMatrix;
22class ByteArray;
23
24namespace QRCode {
25
26class Version;
27class FormatInformation;
28
29/**
30* @author Sean Owen
31*/
32class BitMatrixParser
33{
34public:
35 /**
36 * @param bitMatrix {@link BitMatrix} to parse
37 * return false if dimension is not >= 21 and 1 mod 4
38 */
39 static const Version* ReadVersion(const BitMatrix& bitMatrix, bool mirrored);
40 static FormatInformation ReadFormatInformation(const BitMatrix& bitMatrix, bool mirrored);
41
42 /**
43 * <p>Reads the bits in the {@link BitMatrix} representing the finder pattern in the
44 * correct order in order to reconstruct the codewords bytes contained within the
45 * QR Code.</p>
46 *
47 * @return bytes encoded within the QR Code
48 * or empty array if the exact number of bytes expected is not read
49 */
50 static ByteArray ReadCodewords(const BitMatrix& bitMatrix, const Version& version);
51};
52
53} // QRCode
54} // ZXing
